title: Top 10 WR Rankings + High Expectations, Captain Mike - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/5
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, the rankings shows begin! Get a deep dive on the top 10 WRs for 2022! How do Cooper Kupp and Justin Jefferson compare to 1st Round running backs? Which of our top 10 ranked wideouts is most likely to be a fantasy football bust? Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 8th, 2022.
